node.title: Five people getting medical help after boat flips in Coromandel
node.content: ["Five people are receiving medical treatment after the boat they were on flipped in the Coromandel on Wednesday afternoon.", "Police are currently responding to the incident, which occurred in the water near the coastal town of Pauanui at about 2:30pm.", "Emergency services had earlier rushed to the scene after being notified.", "Police say the five people onboard the boat have \"been accounted for\" and are each receiving medical attention.", "They will provide an update on their status in due course."]
